data.description: Welcome to 4234 Quail Creek Drive! This stunning house is now available for sale.  With 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, this spacious property offers a comfortable and luxurious living experience.    Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the elegant hardwood floors that flow throughout the entire home. The kitchen boasts beautiful granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, making it a chef's dream come true. The main floor features a master bedroom with additional space for an office or sitting area, providing versatility and convenience.  The master bedroom also offers direct access to the back deck, allowing you to enjoy the serene surroundings.  The family room and living room both showcase coffered ceilings, adding a touch of sophistication to the space.  Upstairs, you'll find a loft area along with three more bedrooms and two full bathrooms, ensuring ample space for family members or guests.  Situated on a cul-de-sac lot spanning an impressive 3.79 acres, this property offers privacy and tranquility in a wooded setting. There is even potential to subdivide the lot into separate parcels if desired.  The covered front porch provides the perfect spot to relax and enjoy your morning coffee or watch the sunset in the evenings.  Additionally, there is an unfinished basement that can be customized to suit your needs, whether it be for extra storage or additional living space.  With a total of 3,020 heated square feet, this house offers plenty of room for everyone to spread out and make themselves at home.  Located in a desirable neighborhood, this property is conveniently situated close to amenities such as shopping centers, restaurants, and schools.  Commuting is made easy with nearby access to major highways.   Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this exceptional property! Schedule a showing today and experience all that 4234 Quail Creek Drive has to offer!
